OL,3,CWRU take control of Cardiff Rugby
OL,4,Cafter club 'temporarily enters
OL,5,Cadministration'
OL,7,FThe Welsh Rugby Union has assumed
OL,8,Fcontrol of Cardiff Rugby after the
OL,9,Fclub was temporarily placed into
OL,10,Fadministration.
OL,12,FCardiff Rugby said: "The decision was
OL,13,Fmade once it became clear that the
OL,14,Fclub's owner, Helford Capital, was
OL,15,Funable to meet its obligations to fund
OL,16,Fthe club as it was contractually
OL,17,Fobliged to do. Immediately following
OL,18,Fappointment, administrators sold the
OL,19,Fclub's business and assets to the WRU."
