OL,7,FCardiff Rugby chair Alun Jones said:
OL,8,F"We are incredibly grateful to the
OL,9,FWelsh Rugby Union for securing our
OL,10,Ffinancial stability and ensuring
OL,11,Fprofessional rugby continues in
OL,12,FCardiff as we approach our 150th
OL,13,Fseason.
OL,15,F"The priority has been securing our
OL,16,Fstaff, the future of the club and the
OL,17,Frugby pathway in the capital city and
OL,18,Fwider region."
