OL,7,FA Notice of Intention (NOI) was filed
OL,8,Fin court on Tuesday, 8 April,
OL,9,Feffectively giving Cardiff Rugby two
OL,10,Fweeks to explore options.
OL,12,FWRU chief executive Abi Tierney said:
OL,13,F"We have been keeping in close contact
OL,14,Fwith the Cardiff Rugby Board for
OL,15,Fseveral months once they became aware
OL,16,Fof the risks to anticipated
OL,17,Fshareholder funding not being
OL,18,Favailable. As a result, the WRU has
OL,19,Fbeen able to move quickly to provide
OL,20,Fsupport for Cardiff.
