OL,5,Cadministration'
OL,7,FIt comes just 16 months after Cardiff
OL,8,Flooked to have secured their long-term
OL,9,Ffuture when Helford Capital Limited's
OL,10,Facquisition of a majority shareholding
OL,11,Fwas approved at a general meeting of
OL,12,Fclub members.
OL,14,FA 99.99 per cent majority voted
OL,15,Fthrough the takeover.
OL,17,FHelford Capital Limited, an investment
OL,18,Fgroup led by businessmen Phil Kempe
OL,19,Fand Neal Griffith, acquired an 84.55
OL,20,Fper cent shareholding.
