OL,7,FCardiff play in the United Rugby
OL,8,FChampionship and are next due to be in
OL,9,Faction on April 19 as part of Welsh
OL,10,Frugby's Judgement Day at the
OL,11,FPrincipality Stadium, when Cardiff
OL,12,Fface the Ospreys and Dragons tackle
OL,13,Fthe Scarlets.
OL,15,FThe latest development, though, will
OL,16,Fsend shockwaves through the sport and
OL,17,Ffollows former English Premiership
OL,18,Fclubs Worcester, Wasps and London
OL,19,FIrish entering administration during
OL,20,Fthe 2022-23 season.
